This directory contains R functions to solve
a linear ODE inverse problem.

"separable_ls.R":
Construct a full linear ODE system to fit given observation data
using separable least-squares algorithm.

"variance_linear_ode.R":
Compute variances of an estimation.

"lasso_linearize.R":
Search for a sparse solution by solving a LASSO problem formulated
by the linearization at a given full estimation.

"gradient.R","objective.R":
Private.

"test/":
Testing programs.

"linear_ode_generation/":
A directory containing R functions for generating data for testing
programs.
One may pull down the scripts from:
  https://github.com/guuuuud/linear_ode_generation
and put them directly in the directory or simply create a symbolic
link pointing to the project.
